title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 27 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 27 2022
description:
Jedediah Bila, former schoolteacher, new mom and author of Dear Hartley, joins Clay and Buck on why she is mad as hell over covid mandates. The stupid things we accepted at the beginning of the pandemic. Raheem Kassam tells C&B he thinks Washington wants war in Ukraine. Deadspin attacks biracial NFL coach as "just another white guy." C&B take calls to end the show.
